Package: EINS
Type: Package
Title: Ensemble of Multiple Multi-Omics Integration Methods 
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Mara", "Zuiderwijk", email = "m.o.zuiderwijk@lumc.nl", 
    role = c("cre", "aut")),
    person("Damien", "Olivier", role = "ctb"),
    person("Yassene", "Mohammed", role = "ctb"))
Description: A package to create an R6 object in which multi-omics integration 
    can be performed using nine methods, and the results combined into ensemble 
    integration findings. Multiple omics datasets can be uploaded in the R6 
    object, after which single-omics analysis, multi-omics integration, ensemble
    integration and result visualization can be performed.
